  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for avahi",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for avahi fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2025-68276: avahi: reachable assertion in `avahi_wide_area_scan_cache` can lead to crash of avahi-daemon (bsc#1256498).\n- CVE-2025-68468: avahi: reachable assertion in `lookup_multicast_callback` can lead to crash of avahi-daemon (bsc#1256499).\n- CVE-2025-68471: avahi: reachable assertion in `lookup_start` can lead to crash of avahi-daemon (bsc#1256500).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
